<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I worked at an investment bank during several =
waves of layoffs, and it always felt odd, because I spent most of my day si=
tting around with my colleagues complaining about our jobs and fantasizing =
about quitting. So when layoffs would come around we=E2=80=99d all be like =
=E2=80=9Chow do we get laid off?=E2=80=9D After all, if you get laid off, y=
ou often get a nice severance package, but if you quit you don=E2=80=99t. O=
f course many of the people who=C2=A0<em>did=C2=A0</em>get laid off didn=E2=
=80=99t want to be laid off. They preferred their jobs to the severance pac=
kage. There were trades to be=C2=A0made, and it is not unheard-of for inves=
tment bankers to volunteer for layoffs: If you want to get laid off, and yo=
ur colleague doesn=E2=80=99t, you can make everyone better off by volunteer=
ing=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/33683779.258399/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL=
2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTItMTMvY2l0aS1vZmZlcnMtcGFydGlhbC1lYXJseS1ib251c2VzLXRv=
LWVuY291cmFnZS1zdGFmZi1kZXBhcnR1cmVzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDEyMTMyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV=
0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMTIxMyZ1dG=
1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB5685fe37" itemprop=3D=
"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  h=
ere=E2=80=99s Citi</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Citigroup Inc. is offering to pay some staffer=
s a portion of their bonuses early if they agree to depart as executives co=
ntinue with their restructuring of the Wall Street giant.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The bank is making the offer to a limited numb=
er of staff, according to people familiar with the matter. In addition to t=
he bonus awards, employees who accept the offer would also be allowed to ke=
ep all of their deferred stock awards, the people said, asking not to be id=
entified discussing personnel information.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Staffers cannot volunteer for the offers becau=
se they are being made to those impacted by Citigroup=E2=80=99s ongoing reo=
rganization, which is focused on restructuring its ranks to fit Chief Execu=
tive Officer Jane Fraser=E2=80=99s strategy for the bank.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you get this offer, should you be offended?=
 Does it mean that they=E2=80=99d like to get rid of you but wanted to star=
t with a gentle nudge? Or should you be thrilled because you get to quit wi=
th your bonus?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also it is mid-December? You have pretty much =
earned your whole bonus at this point? Sure you get it early by quitting no=
w instead of in March (=E2=80=9CCitigroup typically awards staffers their b=
onuses in February=E2=80=9D), but it=E2=80=99s not=C2=A0<em>that=C2=A0</em>=
good a deal. Getting half a bonus for quitting in May would be an incentive=
; getting =E2=80=9Ca portion of your bonus=E2=80=9D for quitting in Decembe=
r is a little insulting.</p>
